The paper discusses techniques related to deep learning and classification, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Given that the paper focuses on the application of deep learning techniques to non-neural network classifiers, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG), followed by computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
